      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Runtime Error Smoke Test\n\nThis graph exists only to test diagnostics.\n\n## What it does\n- contains one graph-owned script node\n- the script throws intentionally\n- diagnostics should show the failing script node id and runtime kind\n\n## How to use it\n1. Open the diagnostics or validation panel.\n2. Load this graph.\n3. If the script does not fire automatically, click **RUN** on the script node.\n4. Confirm the panel shows a runtime/script diagnostic for `diagnostics-runtime-smoke-script`."
      }
